description:
An open source unofficial USOS app, for students in Poland An open source unofficial USOS app, for students in Poland. Here you can
  • set and receive notifications about upcoming classes
  • view your grades
  • view your test results
  • check your class schedule
  • see the academic year calendar
  • fill out university surveys
  • send emails to university staff
Currently supported universities
  • ...
    • -Uniwersytet Jagielloński
  • ...
    • -Politechnika Wrocławska
  • ...
    • -Chrześcijańska Akademia Teologiczna w Warszawie.
